    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i tried looking at the flight board but it's just total chaos right now, everyone is running around and the staff look overwhelmed. it's like the whole terminal is just falling apart. any advice on how to handle the crowd or the lines at the service desk so i don't waste even more time?",
